\n得米六五 會唔會好難學得好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會<br />\n<br />\n巴西柔術同泰拳都可以試下<br />\n你可以去Youtube search下Sean Chai，佢得米六左右，但係秦國歷史上其中一個最勁嘅泰拳手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f47cd04c30d70222d8ce6b14a6a2dce197a681","tid":8612,"uid":5851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"Sean chai啲動作唔係人人做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce78d8b76fc1164b746ea87dfa3f86a87cb089eb","tid":8612,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"學馬氣功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a8c43650adade21336b358fc81aab77e718aad","tid":8612,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db968fe6ca55304d3667a99223a75bd5ebeddff0","tid":8612,"uid":37420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"點睇八極拳？"},{"pid":"c99028cc3e6e7b0d7a5cc74e22d010270ae66680","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sean chai啲動作唔係人人做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個當然啦<br />\n學每一種武術都要經過長年累月嘅刻苦訓練，先會有機會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f3bfa246b2dc251735b70ebe829b82abe3b4d0","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇八極拳？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇接觸過，但聽聞以前好多亞洲國家元首嘅保鏢都係高手"},{"pid":"9c278fba0bd67c44fec3b3892f270f050a04906d","tid":8612,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點睇八極拳？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇接觸過，但聽聞以前好多亞洲國家元首嘅保鏢都係高手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩特別，內外家中間。有d內家既風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b0c98b0c57a3589bb7d3a92747bca981ac49ec","tid":8612,"uid":25340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"樓主你幾齒開始練？"},{"pid":"321aeb085a9d64df6e914dc02ba6de36dd5d5b05","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你幾齒開始練？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六歳開始學跆拳道同boxing"},{"pid":"87b050d7ce9eab30b195da3c4f03f64e2d3afca7","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"呢度係咪無乜習武JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96ed87ce352c712206cd3628cddbc71f556cc46","tid":8612,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度係咪無乜習武JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b701d0bbf8c54908d208d70c1200f7d6d6ea277","tid":8612,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實泰拳同散打邊個好d<br />\n同埋想學泰拳有冇咩要注意？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難比較<br />\n即係啲人問李小龍好打定泰臣好打啲咁<br />\n<br />\n不過個人睇法最強立技都係泰拳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n計埋俾插眼打喉呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d35e1e39cfd5d8192d8a0a4e422ec278d73fab2","tid":8612,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"有冇試過係出面比人迫到你出手？"},{"pid":"fe3f7aa15084c9708007a19a21403ffc7de46932","tid":8612,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寸勁係真定假？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真<br />\n<br />\n最出名可以話係李小龍<br />\n<br />\n（不過我對中國武術唔算太熟，如果有錯勿屌）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEsgKx-BFa7E&d=hHFbq%2F4vxrP6tvKf92iQm8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b71e0dfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無可能一掌打個玻璃酒樽既口，樽身無事，而樽底破裂呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個以我所知係有可能<br />\n<br />\n但我未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以前見過最誇張係蔡李佛師傅徒手切豬，真係識郁果啲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以詳細d咁形容下佢點樣切豬<br />\n講下d細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1bf4d27bfa4203889852fe6859995ed881f688","tid":8612,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寸勁係真定假？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真<br />\n<br />\n最出名可以話係李小龍<br />\n<br />\n（不過我對中國武術唔算太熟，如果有錯勿屌）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEsgKx-BFa7E&d=hHFbq%2F4vxrP6tvKf92iQm8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b71e0dfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無可能一掌打個玻璃酒樽既口，樽身無事，而樽底破裂呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個以我所知係有可能<br />\n<br />\n但我未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以前見過最誇張係蔡李佛師傅徒手切豬，真係識郁果啲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以詳細d咁形容下佢點樣切豬<br />\n講下d細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如佢用咩招 個招威力同傷口係點 打左落隻豬度隻豬既傷口又點 隻豬有咩反應"},{"pid":"a9104872e4e839a8ea7496610d6e1f5a2c5c6db4","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實泰拳同散打邊個好d<br />\n同埋想學泰拳有冇咩要注意？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難比較<br />\n即係啲人問李小龍好打定泰臣好打啲咁<br />\n<br />\n不過個人睇法最強立技都係泰拳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n計埋俾插眼打喉呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係秦拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n秦拳係古時秦國人打將用<br />\n<br />\n跆拳道同空手道柔道果啲係運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講可以咁理解"},{"pid":"09bc6f3cec542081ec16e91e932fd256b23d1252","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過係出面比人迫到你出手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我唔會出手，除非真係有人打刧我，或姐其他人需要幫手<br />\n<br />\n我記得幾年前我個教練比兩個人揸刀打刧，佢兩下elbow果兩條友已經訓低左，個頭不停出血，之後我阿sir報警送左兩條友去醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a111c125d4fa34c839524359792d5b1ef825004b","tid":8612,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"想防身學咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對方有刀都走得甩就得，唔使打得贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a4d1e30ab302a0a3652eb3308c2923e23d4b75","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><b