Fbq%2F4vxrP6tvKf92iQm8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f0d39619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/amwjPLCfqhY</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇下master wong啲片，唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6422b890130c7e8ab8c105905623815a7f6bf2f","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf8f5b4594490da7e463a55a29c75ce98a9bfd4","tid":8612,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寸勁係真定假？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真<br />\n<br />\n最出名可以話係李小龍<br />\n<br />\n（不過我對中國武術唔算太熟，如果有錯勿屌）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEsgKx-BFa7E&d=hHFbq%2F4vxrP6tvKf92iQm8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b71e0dfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無可能一掌打個玻璃酒樽既口，樽身無事，而樽底破裂呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個以我所知係有可能<br />\n<br />\n但我未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以前見過最誇張係蔡李佛師傅徒手切豬，真係識郁果啲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以詳細d咁形容下佢點樣切豬<br />\n講下d細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如佢用咩招 個招威力同傷口係點 打左落隻豬度隻豬既傷口又點 隻豬有咩反應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢用蔡李佛普通果啲手法，詳細唔太記得清楚，因為十幾年前嘅事，我記得佢一切落去果下隻豬條頸斷開左一半，爆哂啲血出嚟，當然隻豬慘叫一聲就完<br />\n<br />\n另外係秦國見過有師傅用knee撞碎唒一大舊石頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef901feea40d32ed61672f4b08d92d1b5e21007","tid":8612,"uid":8994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寸勁係真定假？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真<br />\n<br />\n最出名可以話係李小龍<br />\n<br />\n（不過我對中國武術唔算太熟，如果有錯勿屌）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEsgKx-BFa7E&d=hHFbq%2F4vxrP6tvKf92iQm8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b71e0dfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EsgKx-BFa7E</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無可能一掌打個玻璃酒樽既口，樽身無事，而樽底破裂呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個以我所知係有可能<br />\n<br />\n但我未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以前見過最誇張係蔡李佛師傅徒手切豬，真係識郁果啲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以詳細d咁形容下佢點樣切豬<br />\n講下d細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如佢用咩招 個招威力同傷口係點 打左落隻豬度隻豬既傷口又點 隻豬有咩反應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢用蔡李佛普通果啲手法，詳細唔太記得清楚，因為十幾年前嘅事，我記得佢一切落去果下隻豬條頸斷開左一半，爆哂啲血出嚟，當然隻豬慘叫一聲就完<br />\n<br />\n另外係秦國見過有師傅用knee撞碎唒一大舊石頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟得好少巴絲打有習武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開親呢類po都好靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"